    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >關於遊戲</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接一晚的纯粹恐怖吧！你将扮演史蒂夫，这是一位在充满黑暗秘密的医院里开始第一班保安工作的守卫。在监控摄像头时，你会遇到一些奇怪的异常现象，必须去调查并解决，但事情并不总是表面那样简单。每一步，你都会越来越接近揭开医院的黑暗过去和你女儿的神秘失踪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用摄像头实时追踪超自然现象。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=712 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/21baf054a1e63887c68d9e0bbe36b733.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当出现异常时，迅速行动：前往异常发生地，调查并找到解决方法，在为时已晚之前解决问题。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/3d67a2eb68b6598655e54135fc148597.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索医院最阴暗的角落，揭开被遗忘的记忆，拼凑出你女儿的真相。在这个压抑的氛围中，每一个阴影都可能致命。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/309bd3884b9fd061c5cfe6eebcafb47b.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但别忘了，你并不孤单。有什么东西在暗处盯着你。更糟糕的是，潜伏在医院里的噩梦并不只是幻觉。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.poster.avif?t=1739981041\" width=740 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.webm?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247990/extras/960f7b64da7926109a4c5cba17b484ab.mp4?t=1739981041\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特點</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸式體驗:</strong> 具大氣感和寫實的圖像，讓恐怖體驗更加深刻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩法:</strong> 本遊戲是一款行走模擬器，具有異常檢測機制。不同於其他遊戲，你需要親自去修復異常。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖:</strong> 遊戲將試圖欺騙並嚇唬你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From the Other Side</strong> 是一款時長在60至90分鐘之間的短篇遊戲。</p></li></ul>",
